name: ARMANDO.
description:
I met Armando when he ran into me on his bike while I was taking photos downtown. His handlebars hit me in the ribs and he fell on top of me. We've become close friends since then.
Since becoming friends, Armando has done nothing but motivate me and believe in what I do. He always tells me I'm doing something special.
Crazy our paths crossed in the most literal sense.
